member.summary:
Format the given object in the invariant culture. This static method may be imported in C# by
using static System.FormattableString; . Within the scope of that import directive an interpolated string may be formatted in the invariant culture by writing, for example,
Invariant($"{{ lat = {latitude}; lon = {longitude} }}")

Format the given object in the current culture. This static method may be imported in C# by
using static System.FormattableString; . Within the scope of that import directive an interpolated string may be formatted in the current culture by writing, for example,
CurrentCulture($"{{ lat = {latitude}; lon = {longitude} }}")
